            <h3>Atal Pension Yojana (APY)</h3>
            <div class="key-features">
                <ul>
                    <li>Eligibility: Individuals aged between 18 and 40 years</li>
                    <li>Contribution: Monthly, quarterly, or semi-annual contributions</li>
                    <li>Pension Amount: Guaranteed monthly pension ranging from ₹1,000 to ₹5,000</li>
                    <li>Tax Benefits: Tax deductions under Section 80CCD of the Income Tax Act</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h3>Post Office Monthly Income Scheme (POMIS)</h3>
            <div class="key-features">
                <ul>
                    <li>Eligibility: Indian citizens, minors (through guardians), and joint accounts</li>
                    <li>Investment Amount: Minimum ₹1,000, maximum ₹9 lakh (single account) or ₹15 lakh (joint account)</li>
                    <li>Interest Rate: 7.4% per annum (as of April 2024)</li>
                    <li>Tenure: 5 years</li>
                </ul>
            </div>


